OL,3,CPressure mounts on Starmer over small
OL,4,Cboat migrants and asylum hotels
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer faces mounting
OL,7,Fpressure over the small boats crisis
OL,8,Fafter protests continued outside
OL,9,Fasylum hotels and a poll suggested
OL,10,Fvoters thought he was failing to grip
OL,11,Fthe problem.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister and his government
OL,14,Fhave set out measures to speed up the
OL,15,Fasylum appeals system to aid the
OL,16,Fremoval of people with no right to be
OL,17,Fin the UK.
