OL,3,CPressure mounts on Starmer over small
OL,4,Cboat migrants and asylum hotels
OL,6,FBut Labour former home secretary Lord
OL,7,FBlunkett said the Government had so
OL,8,Ffar failed to offer a "comprehensive
OL,9,Fanswer or an understandable narrative"
OL,10,Fon tackling the crisis.
OL,12,FSo far this year a record 28,076
OL,13,Fpeople have crossed the English
OL,14,FChannel in small boats, 46% more than
OL,15,Fin the same period in 2024.
OL,17,FProtests at sites housing asylum
OL,18,Fseekers continued over the weekend and
OL,19,Fthe Government is braced for further
OL,20,Flegal fights over the use of hotels.
