OL,6,FLord Blunkett, who has suggested
OL,7,Ftemporarily suspending elements of the
OL,8,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,9,Fand the UN Refugee Convention to deal
OL,10,Fwith the problem, said Sir Keir had to
OL,11,Fbe "radical" in his approach.
OL,13,FA YouGov poll for The Times found that
OL,14,F71% per cent of voters believe the
OL,15,FPrime Minister is handling the asylum
OL,16,Fhotel issue badly, including 56% of
OL,17,FLabour supporters.
