OL,6,F"At the moment the issue is so toxic
OL,7,Fand beginning to get out of the
OL,8,FGovernment's grip to the point it is
OL,9,Fvery hard to bring it back. A further
OL,10,Fpackage of actions is absolutely vital
OL,11,Fto start controlling both the public
OL,12,Fnarrative and the delivery."
OL,14,FBut Scottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,15,Frejected the idea of shelving human
OL,16,Frights protections to tackle the
OL,17,Fproblem.
OL,19,FHe said the situation was "complex,
OL,20,Fit's difficult" and "there is no one
OL,21,Fsilver bullet".
