OL,6,FMr Sarwar told BBC Radio 4's
OL,7,FWestminster Hour: "I think we have to
OL,8,Faccept the European Convention on
OL,9,FHuman Rights.
OL,11,F"I think we should be working with our
OL,12,Finternational partners around how we
OL,13,Fstrengthen each other and try and
OL,14,Faddress some of the issues
OL,15,Fcollectively. But we should be
OL,16,Fprotecting the European Convention on
OL,17,FHuman Rights.
OL,19,F"We have got to fix the broader
OL,20,Fsystemic issues, which is why we have
OL,21,Fa failed immigration system right now."
