OL,6,F"And I think, for those easy solutions
OL,7,Fsome political parties want to have,
OL,8,Fto blame the migrants or blame the
OL,9,Fmigrant hotels, I think, undermines
OL,10,Fthe legitimate hard work that needs to
OL,11,Fhappen to fix the immigration system,
OL,12,Ffix the asylum system, fix our NHS and
OL,13,Fbuild more houses across the country."
OL,15,FOfficial figures released earlier this
OL,16,Fmonth showed a total of 111,084 people
OL,17,Fapplied for asylum in the UK in the
OL,18,Fyear to June 2025, the highest number
OL,19,Ffor any 12-month period since current
OL,20,Frecords began in 2001.
