OL,6,FThe record level of applications comes
OL,7,Fas the backlog of people waiting for
OL,8,Fan initial decision on their claims
OL,9,Fdropped to 90,812 at the end of June.
OL,11,FThere were 32,059 asylum seekers in UK
OL,12,Fhotels by the end of the same month.
OL,14,FLabour has promised to end the use of
OL,15,Fthe sites by 2029.
OL,17,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,18,F"completely unacceptable" delays in
OL,19,Fthe appeals process left failed asylum
OL,20,Fseekers in the system for years.
