OL,3,CPressure mounts on Starmer over small
OL,4,Cboat migrants and asylum hotels
OL,6,FThe Government has put forward plans
OL,7,Ffor a new system where a panel of
OL,8,Findependent adjudicators, rather than
OL,9,Ftribunal judges, deals with appeals
OL,10,Fover asylum decisions.
OL,12,FThere are about 51,000 asylum appeals
OL,13,Fwaiting to be heard, taking on average
OL,14,Fmore than a year to reach a decision,
OL,15,Fwith the backlog now thought to be the
OL,16,Fbiggest cause of pressure in the
OL,17,Fasylum accommodation system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
