OL,6,FThe Home Secretary said the overhaul
OL,7,Fwould result in a system which is
OL,8,F"swift, fair and independent, with
OL,9,Fhigh standards in place".
OL,11,FHowever, the Refugee Council's Imran
OL,12,FHussain said: "The fastest way to
OL,13,Fspeed up asylum appeals is to get
OL,14,Fdecisions right first time.
OL,16,F"But at the moment, nearly half of
OL,17,Fappeals are successful, meaning that
OL,18,Fthe initial decision was wrong."
